Annotations.Annotation: Cube Schema for CCRS - General Profile

ExpressionView.SQL: select b.ISO2 as ISO2, c.REGION as REGION, b.NAME as NAME, b.ID as BASE_COUNTRY_ID from BASE_COUNTRY b, CATEGORY c where b.ISO2 = c.COUNTRY AND c.DTYPE = 'CountryRegion'

select M.*, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN M.NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as NON_RESIDENT_AGENCY_COUNT from CP1UNCTMEMBER M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

SELECT M.*, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY FROM CP1UNCGMEMBER M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

select M.ID, M.PARENT_ID, M.AGENCY_ID, CASE WHEN M.NAME IS NULL THEN '' ELSE M.NAME END as NAME, CASE WHEN M.EMAIL IS NULL THEN '' ELSE M.EMAIL END as EMAIL, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP1OMTMEMBER M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

select M.*, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN M.RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as RESULTS_GROUP_DEFINED_BYSOP_COUNT, CASE WHEN M.JOINT_WORKPLAN = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as JOINT_WORKPLAN_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP1INTERAGENCY_GROUP M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

select M.ID, M.COUNTRY_ID as CC_COUNTRY_ID, M.INCOME_STATUS_ID as CC_INCOME_STATUS_ID, M.YEAR_OF_BECOMINGDAO as CC_YEAR_OF_BECOMINGDAO, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CASE WHEN M.DAO = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as DAO_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY from CP1COUNTRY M, CP1GENERAL_PROFILE CP1, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE M.PARENT_ID = CP1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR

select CP1.ID, CP1.DESIGNATION, CP1.ENTITY_YEAR, CP1.COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.SECONDARY_COUNTRY_INCOME_STATUS_ID, CP1.YEAR_OF_OFFICIAL_REQUEST, CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID, CP1.PROJECTED_TOTALBOSSAVINGS_THIS_YEAR, CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID, CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID, CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID, CP1.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID, CASE WHEN cp1.OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as OFFICIAL_REQUEST_DAO_COUNTRY, CASE WHEN cp1.DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as DAO_VISION_NOTE_ROADMAP_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1.COVER_MORE_THAN_ONE_COUNTRY = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as COVER_MORE_THAN_ONE_COUNTRY_COUNT, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12561 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15q_YES_FULLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12562 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15q_YES_PARTIALLY, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP1q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP2q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP3q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP4q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP5q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP6q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP7q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP8q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP9q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP10q_NO, CASE WHEN HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP11q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP12q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP13q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP14q_NO, CASE WHEN HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID = 12563 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as SOP15q_NO, HAS_JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN_ID, HAS_ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS_ID, HAS_SIGNEDUNDAFOUTCOME_LEVEL_LEGAL_TEXT_ID, HAS_JOINT_ANNUAL_WORK_PLANS_ID, HAS_RESULTS_GROUPS_ID, HAS_MID_TERM_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID, HAS_ANNUAL_COMM_BUDGET_FRAMEWORK_ID, HAS_JOINT_RESOURCE_MOBILISATION_STRATEGY_ID, HAS_COMMITMENT_AND_INCETIVES_TOWARDS_COMMON_RESULTS_ID, HAS_EMPOWEREDUNCTJOINT_DECISIONS_PROGR_ACTIVITIES_ID, HASBOSSTRATEGY_ID, HAS_EMPOWERED_OPS_MANAGEMENT_TEAM_ID, HAS_OPERATIONS_COSTS_BUDGETS_INTEGRATED_ID, HAS_JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY_ID, HAS_COUNTRY_COMM_GROUP_ID, cp1joint.GOVERNMENT_ROLE_ID, cp1joint.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID as SOP1_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1joint.HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE CASE WHEN cp1joint.HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW = FALSE THEN 0 ELSE -1 END END as HAS_ANNUAL_REVIEW, CASE WHEN cp1annual.REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE CASE WHEN cp1annual.REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV = FALSE THEN 0 ELSE -1 END END as REPORT_SUBMITTED_TO_GOV, cp1annual.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID as SOP2_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID, CASE WHEN cp1annual.REPORT_PUBLICLY_AVAILABLE = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE 0 END as REPORT_PUBLICLY_AVAILABLE_COUNT, cp1annual.REPORT_PUBLISHING_MODALITY_ID, CASE WHEN cp1jointstrategy.BUDGETED_WORKPLAN = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE CASE WHEN cp1jointstrategy.BUDGETED_WORKPLAN = FALSE THEN 0 ELSE -1 END END as BUDGETED_WORKPLAN, CASE WHEN cp1jointstrategy.UNDAF_BASED_OR_EQUIVALENT = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE CASE WHEN cp1jointstrategy.UNDAF_BASED_OR_EQUIVALENT = FALSE THEN 0 ELSE -1 END END as UNDAF_BASED_OR_EQUIVALENT_COUNT, CASE WHEN cp1jointstrategy.REPORT_INUNCOUNTRY_RESULTS_REPORT = TRUE THEN 1 ELSE CASE WHEN cp1jointstrategy.REPORT_INUNCOUNTRY_RESULTS_REPORT = FALSE THEN 0 ELSE -1 END END as REPORT_INUNCOUNTRY_RESULTS_REPORT_COUNT, cp1jointstrategy.PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID as SOP14_PARTIAL_IMPLEMENTATION_DETAILS_ID from CP1GENERAL_PROFILE cp1, CP1JOINT_OVERSIGHT_OWNERSHIP_GOVUN cp1joint, CP1ANNUAL_REPORTING_JOINTUNRESULTS cp1annual, CP1JOINT_COMM_STRATEGY cp1jointstrategy, BASE_COUNTRY bc, V_CP_VALIDATED_DESIGNATIONS v WHERE cp1joint.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID AND cp1annual.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID AND cp1jointstrategy.PARENT_ID = cp1.ID AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'AQ' AND CP1.DESIGNATION != 'DOCO' AND CP1.DESIGNATION = bc.ISO2 AND CP1.DESIGNATION = v.DESIGNATION AND v.ENTITY_YEAR = CP1.ENTITY_YEAR
